  • 方法详细资料

    • CSVtoList1

      public static ArrayList<Info> CSVtoList1(String csvFilePath)
      Description: This is the function to read a file in csv format and change it to an info arraylist and return it.
      参数:
      csvFilePath - the file path of the .csv file

    • addStudentInfo

      public static void addStudentInfo(ArrayList<Info> infos, String csvFilePath, String ID, String classID, String name, String PIN)
      Description: This method is for adding student in arraylist and write it into the csv file
      参数:
      infos - the arraylist which store all the information inside.
      csvFilePath - the file path of the csv file that you want to change
      ID - student identification number, which is one of the import attribute inside an element of info arraylist.
      classID - student class ID number, which is one of the import attribute inside an element of info arraylist.
      name - student name which is one of the import attribute inside an element of info arraylist.
      PIN - student password to log in, which is one of the import attribute inside an element of info arraylist.

    • removeStudentInfo

      public static void removeStudentInfo(ArrayList<Info> infos, String csvFilePath, String ID)
      Description: This method is for removing student in arraylist, just by his/her ID
      参数:
      infos - the arraylist which store all the information inside.
      csvFilePath - the file path of the csv file that you want to change
      ID - student identification number. It is used to search in all the elements in info arraylist and do the match.

    • updateStudentInfo

      public static void updateStudentInfo(ArrayList<Info> infos, String csvFilePath, String ID, String newClassID, String newName, String newPIN)
      Description: This method is for updating student in arraylist, first of all we search student by ID, then update all the attributes inside.
      参数:
      infos - the arraylist which store all the information inside.
      csvFilePath - the file path of the csv file that you want to change
      ID - the student ID number that you want to update.
      newClassID - the updated class ID
      newName - the updated name
      newPIN - the updated password
